{"tid":2441311,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"孔繁毅：第一位死者即使不接種疫苗 相信病情都會在短期內惡化 科興非不同意長者打 僅不建議","createTime":"2021-03-10T15:00:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T04:46:10.000Z","uid":270961,"like":8,"dislike":112,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"122459d080d480863ab60a51288c0f7134919e30","tid":2441311,"uid":270961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:00:35.000Z","msg":"首名死者好想打針 未講清楚病情<br />\n<br />\n孔指，疫苗中心有醫護人員駐場，市民接有責任如實反映自身病況，此前曾有市民因病情而被拒絕打針。對於首宗死亡個案死者患冠心病卻仍然成功打針，孔認為當中不涉及失誤，稱當時醫護人員有按規定詢問，但死者「好想接種疫苗」，當時未有明確講述自身病情。他又強調，死者心血管栓塞問題十分嚴重，即使不接種疫苗，相信病情都會在短期內惡化，又指疫苗並無加速惡化。<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n孔繁毅：科興非不同意長者打 僅不建議<br />\n<br />\n本港疫苗接種計劃安排60歲以上長者為優先人群，做法與內地大不同，孔繁毅稱內地並非認為長者不適合接種，只是兩地接種策略不同。他解釋，科興不建議長者接種，只因臨床數據較少，但本港專家審視後認為18歲以上人士可以安全接種，加上長者屬於高風險感染人群，因此安排優先接種。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210310/KDAUVBQAUBDO5CX635LJTIXDIQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210310%2FKDAUVBQAUBDO5CX635LJTIXDIQ%2F&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPj2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=19b11c05\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210310%2FKDAUVBQAUBDO5CX635LJTIXDIQ%2F&h=475c9ea5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210310/KDAUVBQAUBDO5CX635LJTIXDIQ/</a>"},{"pid":"d93033805fb9049f5669e5690e1724319ab099e8","tid":2441311,"uid":270961,"like":81,"dislike":0,"score":81,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:03:54.000Z","msg":"孔繁毅To廢老：呼籲長者盡早接種疫苗，但係你哋打完死咗唔關我事，因為我一早唔建議你哋打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f40553234eb07bd594980093419b0ce64787cd5e","tid":2441311,"uid":141268,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:05:10.000Z","msg":"孔手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb192fbfd7e249437826d3856c26c02c4c24d820","tid":2441311,"uid":11663,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:05:22.000Z","msg":"科興建議18至59打，佢又唔去打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9075bd01dc0b9ae45cb63e4d84e956c4ec154c50","tid":2441311,"uid":42700,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:05:56.000Z","msg":"難聽過粗口"},{"pid":"4958e66a177f7d5befe6f4f2771dbde2d0a382da","tid":2441311,"uid":92661,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:06:16.000Z","msg":"即係人始終要死，根本同疫苗冇關"},{"pid":"d88253387000f9011c5ad93b5c45bad12fe04ab6","tid":2441311,"uid":42820,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:07:43.000Z","msg":"孔繁毅(打BioNTech）"},{"pid":"8e25a435be11c7aa9357b249f116c816419cee50","tid":2441311,"uid":3241,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:07:44.000Z","msg":"孔同志， 多謝你推動藍屍去打科興<br />\n比許匪樹昌， 袁匪國勇呢類走狗好得多"},{"pid":"8d46eb6858c602de519ddcba2219d36d488a9f7e","tid":2441311,"uid":125385,"like":63,"dislike":0,"score":63,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:07:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RFnitcd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRFnitcd.gif&h=c37655bf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3688f0646e1760bdf6219cdcf056d9b3a7ed9c7a","tid":2441311,"uid":222614,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4958e66a177f7d5befe6f4f2771dbde2d0a382da","tid":2441311,"uid":92661,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:06:16.000Z","msg":"即係人始終要死，根本同疫苗冇關"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:11:16.000Z","msg":"但政府又唔會話「高危嘅都係有佢死，無謂嘥左支疫苗」<br />\n<br />\n但明明全世界都唔夠疫苗用 ....<br />\n<br />\n外國又係咁，即使啲老人同長期病患者病到就死咁都照幫佢地打<br />\n但另一方面又話唔夠疫苗用<br />\n全世界政府都失去理智 ...."},{"pid":"e1fc977c87fb22adf841bad0ffdb9237dcb6ef03","tid":2441311,"uid":55913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:13:59.000Z","msg":"班傻閪愛國早死係正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfa4e13e8103150b330f383cc2129fc1b5e3db54","tid":2441311,"uid":120983,"like"