:0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T17:51:52.000Z","msg":"完美演繹人終須一死。"},{"pid":"c76f66dacffad02282534b911bffdc450e853e3b","tid":2441311,"uid":31946,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T20:26:13.000Z","msg":"責任全在死者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完。"},{"pid":"cae4014005a197e72a2b1b3a8f749b04968ccd43","tid":2441311,"uid":31946,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T20:26:41.000Z","msg":"後生<br />\n中年<br />\n老年<br />\n<br />\n都終須一死，唔關疫苗事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45340ca66915fa9b49402db85b952da005dbf7c9","tid":2441311,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T20:29:13.000Z","msg":"其實人終有一死 係早定遲<br />\n咁我打完就釘 咁我打唔打好"},{"pid":"38a4945ac2e1f617d7e03355345b0261cb19edb1","tid":2441311,"uid":255489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"122459d080d480863ab60a51288c0f7134919e30","tid":2441311,"uid":270961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:00:35.000Z","msg":"首名死者好想打針 未講清楚病情<br />\n<br />\n孔指，疫苗中心有醫護人員駐場，市民接有責任如實反映自身病況，此前曾有市民因病情而被拒絕打針。對於首宗死亡個案死者患冠心病卻仍然成功打針，孔認為當中不涉及失誤，稱當時醫護人員有按規定詢問，但死者「好想接種疫苗」，當時未有明確講述自身病情。他又強調，死者心血管栓塞問題十分嚴重，即使不接種疫苗，相信病情都會在短期內惡化，又指疫苗並無加速惡化。<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n孔繁毅：科興非不同意長者打 僅不建議<br />\n<br />\n本港疫苗接種計劃安排60歲以上長者為優先人群，做法與內地大不同，孔繁毅稱內地並非認為長者不適合接種，只是兩地接種策略不同。他解釋，科興不建議長者接種，只因臨床數據較少，但本港專家審視後認為18歲以上人士可以安全接種，加上長者屬於高風險感染人群，因此安排優先接種。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210310/KDAUVBQAUBDO5CX635LJTIXDIQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210310%2FKDAUVBQAUBDO5CX635LJTIXDIQ%2F&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPj2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=19b11c05\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210310%2FKDAUVBQAUBDO5CX635LJTIXDIQ%2F&h=475c9ea5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210310/KDAUVBQAUBDO5CX635LJTIXDIQ/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T20:39:16.000Z","msg":"認住呢條醫蓄"},{"pid":"f88bcdfc2efbafa0465b450b7054a5b27379f236","tid":2441311,"uid":36901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f37023f45d432a1526daa4f37886ac2f8139eb95","tid":2441311,"uid":365791,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:18:05.000Z","msg":"都話咗係廢佬清除計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T20:40:08.000Z","msg":"簡直係愛國者清除計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef1e785f6490781b63fc12ee856df64739a8a7e9","tid":2441311,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d93033805fb9049f5669e5690e1724319ab099e8","tid":2441311,"uid":270961,"like":81,"dislike":0,"score":81,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T15:03:54.000Z","msg":"孔繁毅To廢老：呼籲長者盡早接種疫苗，但係你哋打完死咗唔關我事，因為我一早唔建議你哋打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T20:46:09.000Z","msg":"要借下面quote嘅說話，去save hk, discuss宣傳，鼓勵人打針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>年年打流感針都死好多人，你點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://lih.kg/aLprbFV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aLprbFV</a>"},{"pid":"ca44429ba9645ed753eced4e54816efb623a754e","tid":2441311,"uid":300006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T23:19:17.000Z","msg":"我都知你遲早會死"},{"pid":"98a040f97a7779f3d20d85f4c47b40ee43551afb","tid":2441311,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T23:20:48.000Z","msg":"有毒氣體無害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif